io.confluent.ksql.query

Interface QueueCallback

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    LimitQueueCallback
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LimitedQueueCallback, UnlimitedQueueCallback

    @ThreadSafe
public interface QueueCallback
    A callback called before and after things are queued.

    Implementations must be thread-safe as they will be called from multiple threads simultaneously.
